      <h2 id="area2" style="margin-top:2.5rem">第二區要不要全包？8 倍的代價值不值得</h2>

      <figure style="margin:1.5rem 0">
        <img src="/images/articles/power-lottery-wheeling-area2.webp"
             srcset="/images/articles/power-lottery-wheeling-area2-768w.webp 768w, /images/articles/power-lottery-wheeling-area2.webp 1376w"
